CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775747465
OL,3,CThief jailed for stealing #2m Faberge
OL,4,Cegg in handbag theft at Soho pub
OL,6,FA thief who swiped a handbag from a
OL,7,FSoho pub containing a Faberge egg and
OL,8,Fwatch set valued at up to three
OL,9,Fmillion dollars (#2.2 million) has
OL,10,Fbeen jailed for more than two years.
OL,12,FEnzo Conticello, 29, took the Givenchy
OL,13,Fhandbag belonging to Rosie Dawson as
OL,14,Fshe stood in the smoking area of the
OL,15,FDog and Duck pub in Bateman Street on
OL,16,FNovember 7, 2024.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775747465
OL,3,CThief jailed for stealing #2m Faberge
OL,4,Cegg in handbag theft at Soho pub
OL,6,FInside the #1,600 bag was an emerald-
OL,7,Fencrusted Faberge egg and Faberge
OL,8,Fwatch belonging to Ms Dawson's
OL,9,Femployers at the Craft Irish Whiskey
OL,10,FCompany, as well as a #1,500 Apple
OL,11,Flaptop, Apple AirPods, a #350 store
OL,12,Fvoucher, keys, Ms Dawson's three bank
OL,13,Fcards, #200 worth of make-up, a
OL,14,FMulberry card holder worth #150, and
OL,15,F#20 in cash.
OL,17,FSouthwark Crown Court heard on
OL,18,FThursday that Conticello was after
OL,19,F"easy money", and he says he handed
OL,20,Fover the bag ` complete with the
OL,21,FFaberge egg and watch ` to buy drugs.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775747465
OL,3,CThief jailed for stealing #2m Faberge
OL,4,Cegg in handbag theft at Soho pub
OL,6,FRecorder Kate Livesey sentenced him to
OL,7,Ftwo years and three months in prison,
OL,8,Ftelling him the "opportunistic" theft
OL,9,Fhad caused "inconvenience and stress"
OL,10,Fto Ms Dawson and her company.
OL,12,F"Ms Dawson described the particular
OL,13,Fshock and panic upon realising a bag
OL,14,Fcontaining items of such particular
OL,15,Fvalue owned by the company had been
OL,16,Fstolen, and the incredible stress this
OL,17,Fincident has caused her," she said.
OL,26,@pD@QOUpD@_O]qD@LOUqD@eO]tD@AOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775747465
OL,3,CThief jailed for stealing #2m Faberge
OL,4,Cegg in handbag theft at Soho pub
OL,6,FAt a hearing in February, Conticello `
OL,7,Falso known as Hakin Boudjenoune `
OL,8,Fpleaded guilty to three charges of
OL,9,Ffraud by false representation and one
OL,10,Fcount of theft.
OL,12,FHe was linked to the handbag theft
OL,13,Fafter trying to use Ms Dawson's stolen
OL,14,Fbank cards in a nearby shop within
OL,15,Fminutes of committing the crime.
OL,17,FProsecutor Julian Winship told the
OL,18,Fsentencing hearing: "On November 7
OL,19,F2024 at just before 10pm, (Ms Dawson)
OL,20,Fwent to the Dog and Duck pub in Soho.
OL,26,@zD@UOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775747465
OL,3,CThief jailed for stealing #2m Faberge
OL,4,Cegg in handbag theft at Soho pub
OL,6,F"She was outside the premises in the
OL,7,Fdesignated smoking area, she put her
OL,8,Fhandbag on the ground in between her
OL,9,Flegs, and a few minutes later she
OL,10,Fnoticed her handbag was no longer
OL,11,Fthere."
OL,13,FThe court heard Ms Dawson had the
OL,14,FFaberge items in her handbag after she
OL,15,Fhad taken them for display at a work
OL,16,Fevent earlier that evening.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775747465
OL,3,CThief jailed for stealing #2m Faberge
OL,4,Cegg in handbag theft at Soho pub
OL,6,FMr Winship said Conticello "wanted to
OL,7,Fobtain some easy cash", and
OL,8,Fprosecutors accept he did not intend
OL,9,Fto steal the Faberge egg and
OL,10,Faccompanying watch.
OL,12,FInsurers have paid out #106,700 to the
OL,13,Fdrinks company for the loss, but the
OL,14,Fprosecutor said there are only seven
OL,15,FFaberge sets ` containing a jewelled
OL,16,Fegg, watch, whisky bottle, cigars and
OL,17,Fhumidor ` in existence.
OL,26,@nD@\OUoD@VO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775747465
OL,3,CThief jailed for stealing #2m Faberge
OL,4,Cegg in handbag theft at Soho pub
OL,6,FThree had been sold for between two to
OL,7,Fthree million dollars each, and the
OL,8,Fcompany was seeking similar amounts
OL,9,Ffor the remaining four sets.
OL,11,FConticello's barrister, Katie Porter-
OL,12,FWindley, told the court he previously
OL,13,Fworked as a chef but lost his job in
OL,14,Fthe Covid pandemic and slipped into
OL,15,Fcocaine addiction.
OL,17,F"On the night in question, it was a
OL,18,Fmoment of opportunity which he took,
OL,19,Fand he is genuinely remorseful for his
OL,20,Fbehaviour," she said.
OL,26,@yD@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775747465
OL,3,CThief jailed for stealing #2m Faberge
OL,4,Cegg in handbag theft at Soho pub
OL,6,F"He gave the bag to someone to
OL,7,Fpurchase drugs. He had a cocaine
OL,8,Faddiction at the time."
OL,10,FWithin minutes of her handbag being
OL,11,Fstolen, Ms Dawson received a fraud
OL,12,Falert on her phone at 10.12pm, showing
OL,13,FConticello had tried to use one of her
OL,14,Fbank cards for a #33.48 purchase at a
OL,15,Fshop in nearby Berwick Street.
OL,17,FTwo further attempts were made to use
OL,18,Fher cards, at 11.30pm and 12.30am, but
OL,19,Fthey had already been cancelled with
OL,20,Fthe banks.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@WO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775747465
OL,3,CThief jailed for stealing #2m Faberge
OL,4,Cegg in handbag theft at Soho pub
OL,6,F"Early on Friday morning, the
OL,7,Fcomplainant received a message on
OL,8,Fsocial media from someone who had
OL,9,Ffound her bank card on the ground
OL,10,Fbetween Soho and Charing Cross," Mr
OL,11,FWinship said.
OL,13,FConticello was arrested for separate
OL,14,Ftheft offences in Belfast in November
OL,15,F2025, more than a year after the
OL,16,Fhandbag theft, and was then linked to
OL,17,Fthe 2024 crime.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775747465
OL,3,CThief jailed for stealing #2m Faberge
OL,4,Cegg in handbag theft at Soho pub
OL,6,FThe court heard the Faberge egg and
OL,7,Fwatch have not been recovered, and Mr
OL,8,FWinship said efforts to seek
OL,9,Fconfiscation or compensation from
OL,10,FConticello will not be pursued.
OL,12,F"It appears to me unlikely that the
OL,13,Fdefendant is a person of means able to
OL,14,Fsatisfy either of these particular
OL,15,Fprosecutorial routes available to us,"
OL,16,Fsaid Mr Winship.
OL,18,FMs Porter-Windley told the court
OL,19,FConticello did not realise how
OL,20,Fvaluable the items were that he had
OL,21,Fstolen.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@fO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775747465
OL,3,CThief jailed for stealing #2m Faberge
OL,4,Cegg in handbag theft at Soho pub
OL,6,FWhen the judge remarked the egg is
OL,7,F"quite extraordinary looking", with an
OL,8,Femerald forming part of its exterior,
OL,9,Fthe defence barrister replied: "It is
OL,10,Fso extraordinary that he wouldn't know
OL,11,Fon the face of it whether that was
OL,12,Fhigh value or not."
OL,14,FShe said Conticello was homeless at
OL,15,Fthe time, and he is currently a "man
OL,16,Fof no means".
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@]O]qD@`OUtD@SO]wD@aOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775747465
OL,3,CThief jailed for stealing #2m Faberge
OL,4,Cegg in handbag theft at Soho pub
OL,6,FThe judge said Conticello, of no fixed
OL,7,Faddress, would ordinarily have been
OL,8,Fordered to pay #3,000 in compensation
OL,9,Fto Ms Dawson, but she would not make
OL,10,Fthe order as he has no way of paying
OL,11,Fit.
OL,13,FHe is set to serve up to half the
OL,14,Fprison term before being released on
OL,15,Flicence.
OL,17,FThe Met Police said it is continuing
OL,18,Fto hunt for the 10cm green and gold
OL,19,Fegg and accompanying watch.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775747465
OL,3,CThief jailed for stealing #2m Faberge
OL,4,Cegg in handbag theft at Soho pub
OL,6,FDetective Constable Arben Morina, who
OL,7,Fis leading the investigation, said:
OL,8,F"Conticello thought nothing of helping
OL,9,Fhimself to someone else's possessions,
OL,10,Fand he now faces a prison sentence as
OL,11,Fa result of his greed.
OL,13,F"This theft has had a significant
OL,14,Fimpact on the victim, who was on her
OL,15,Fway home from a work event when she
OL,16,Fwas targeted.
OL,18,F"The defendant never explained to the
OL,19,Fpolice what he did with the expensive
OL,20,Fjewellery.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
