PN,40314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775747465
OL,3,CThief jailed for stealing #2m Faberge
OL,4,Cegg in handbag theft at Soho pub
OL,6,F"Our investigation to find the egg and
OL,7,Fthe watch is ongoing and we'd urge
OL,8,Fanyone with information to contact us."
